## âœ… Functional Requirements
Priority levels: (Must,Should,Could)

| ID     | Requirement Description                                | Priority | Status  |
|--------|--------------------------------------------------------|----------|---------|
| FR-01  | Students can mark attendance via sharing location      | Must     | Draft   |
| FR-02  | Lecturers can view and edit attendance records         | Must     | Draft   |
| FR-03  | Admins can generate attendance reports                 | Should   | Draft   |
| FR-04  | Students can view their attendance history             | Should   | Draft   |
| FR-05  | System sends alerts for low attendance                 | Could    | Draft   |

