## âš™ï¸ Non-Functional Requirements
Priority levels: (Must,Should,Could)

| ID     | Requirement Description                                | Priority | Status  |
|--------|--------------------------------------------------------|----------|---------|
| NFR-01 | System must be mobile responsive                       | Must     | Draft   |
| NFR-02 | Attendance data must be encrypted                      | Must     | Draft   |
| NFR-03 | System should support 1000+ concurrent users           | Should   | Draft   |
| NFR-04 | Login should support OTP for added security            | Could    | Draft   |

